summary: Ever wonder how an NPC got to look so different? It's from a mod usually. So rather than mod the mod I just exported Muiri's vanilla state from CK.
descriptionHtml:
Ever wonder how an NPC got to look so different? It's from a mod usually. So rather than mod the mod I just exported Muiri's vanilla state from CK. I actually quite like the vanilla Muiri. So this changes her back to vanilla. Just make sure it's last in your load order so it can over write any other mods that change Muiri's appearance.

Known issue: Yes, I know that Muiri has face paint in the vanilla game, but it isn't in the screen shot. Though it doesn't make any sense, because the face paint is listed in CK under face parts and with the right color, but it doesn't show up. If anyone wants to try to fix this, you are more than welcome to.
author: Landon783
